p_1
 p_1\dot p_1+p_2\dot p_2=0\implies p_1^2+p_2^2=\text{constant}=a^2+b^2. 
 -B\,p_1\dot p_1+A\,p_3\dot p_3=0\implies -B\,p_1^2+A\,p_3^2=\text{constant}=-B\,a^2+A\,c^2. 
